This is NAP version 2.0, beta release 3.  There are important changes
between the first beta version and this one,  so please  read the en-
tire manual. I wrote two manuals, an English and a German one:

The English manual has the suffix  ".doc".  Since my English isn't so
good there might be mistakes. It would be kind if someone would proof
read this manual.

It seems to be silly to make three beta releases of the same program.
But when I finished beta version 1 and 2,  I had no chance  to get it
to you.  Nonetheless I did not stop working,  so the new version must
got a new name, and since the version below was still not tested,  it
became a new beta release.  But this is the last beta release for NAP
2.00. I expect your bug reports and if there come none (unbelievable)
or when I have fixed all bugs,  the REAL 2.00 version will be send to
you.

